quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,"Alif, laam, raa. ∆äen ko Aayeeje Deftere e janngeteende …ìannginnde"
  15,2,Na waawi Heefer…ìe …ìen yeloyto sinno …ìe laatino juul…ìe
  15,3,"Accu …ìe, …ìe √±aama …ìe dakmitoo, yela soklina …ìe; arma …ìe anndoya"
  15,4,"Men halkaali saare woo, si wanaa hara no woodani nde happu anndaa…óo"
  15,5,"Mofte woo adotaako lajal mun, …ìe nennantaake kadi"
  15,6,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Ko an yo mo Deftere nden jippinaa e mun, an ko a feetu…óo"
  15,7,"Ko ha…óno addanaa men Malaa'ikaa…ìe, si a laatike goongu…óo"
  15,8,"Men jippinirtaa Malaa'ika si wanaa fii goonga; …ìe wonataa ontuma, nennantee…ìe"
  15,9,"Menen Men jippinii Deftere nden, Menen kadi ko Men reenoo…ìe nde"
  15,10,"Gom…óii Men nuliino ado maa, e le√±i adinoo…ìe"
  15,11,Nulaa…óo (woo) araali e ma…ì…ìe si wanaa …ìe jalkitay mo
  15,12,Ko wano nii Men naadiri …óum e …ìer…óe bon…ìe …ìen
  15,13,"∆Åe gom…óintaa nde, gom…óii sunna aram…ìe …ìen yawtiino"
  15,14,"Hay si Men udditanno …ìe damal ka kammu, …ìe wa…ótini hi…ìe ∆¥awra heen"
  15,15,"…ìe wi'ayno: \"Anndee gite amen …óen hippa. Wurin ko men yim…ìe mbil…óaa…ìe"
